name: UnicornLand
overview: Unicornland is an 8-episode webseries about Annie, who explores her sexuality post-divorce by dating couples.  ...Over drinks, at dinner, and in bed.  Each episode features a date with a new couple, from Williamsburg hipsters, to Wall Street power duos, to Bushwick burners, as Annie becomes not just sexually active, but activated.
